V2.89 - Update for Google Ads

V2.88 - Updated under the hood. New features in the works.

V2.86 - Ad fixes

V2.85 - Fix for Previous Track being displayed instead of Next Track

V2.84 - Fixed some Note 3 specific stuff, fix for crash when UI in background

V2.83 - Added Note 3 sensor to Sensor Setup area, new Spanish Translation, probably makes a lot more sense now. Thanks Rodrigo!!, 
Fixed timing changes not showing up in the Sensor Setup, added Google Analytics

V2.80 - Added in support for Samsung Note 3's Left/Right/Up/Down gestures! Should work on S4 after Android 4.3 update too. 
bug fix for vibrate still going off in limited modes

V2.75: Added in Launch on Car Dock Connect option, updated visuals, added Korean language

V2.70: Added in Quick Setup to beginning. Added option to change sensor timing for slower sensors. Should work much better on HTC phones.

V2.66: Fix for issue with app not loading on some phones.. problem in advertiser's code. Ugh. Sorry.

V2.65: Fixed speakerphone(during call controls) not starting on some phones
Bug fixes
Start up page before ad loads

V2.61: Fix for crash on exit bug

... Let me know if I broke anything!
